{"id":92393,"type":2,"name":"ベイベーばあちゃん","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/af/f6/92393_Mj778.jpg","summary":"神宮寺亜美歌（じんぐうじ あみか）は、アイドルを目指す小学5年生。ある日、おばあちゃんの神宮寺ウメが亡くなったという知らせを聞く。おばあちゃんは礼儀に厳しい人で亜美歌は時に反発していたが、「もう少し優しくしてやれば良かったかなあ？」と後悔する。\r\n数日後、亜美歌に待望の妹、小梅が生まれるが、その小梅に死んだはずのおばあちゃんが憑依してしまった。おばあちゃんはどうやら、亜美歌に「THE PERFECT JINGUJIコンテスト」に出場し、優勝して自分の財産を継いでもらいたいために、戻ってきた。\r\nしかし亜美歌はアイドルになりたいので、コンテストに興味はない。結局、亜美歌は物語終盤まで、コンテストに出場する気はなかったのだが……。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>宝贝婆婆</li><li><span>话数: </span>53</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>2002年4月8日</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/2974\">JINCO</a></li><li><span>人物原案: </span><a href=\"/person/2974\">JINCO</a></li><li><span>背景美术: </span><a href=\"/person/11891\">スタジオじゃっく</a></li><li><span>播放电视台: </span>NHK教育テレビ</li><li><span>播放结束: </span>2002年7月11日</li>","collection":{"wish":3,"collect":2,"on_hold":1,"dropped":6},"tags":[{"name":"冷门","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":354993,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/354993","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":354994,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/354994","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":354995,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/354995","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":354996,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/354996","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":354997,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/354997","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":354998,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/354998","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":354999,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/354999","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":355000,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/35500